	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />i'd say the intention would be to create a &quot;family friendly&quot; setting for parents who want to share the experience with their kids, without feeling they might need to talk seriously about what is experienced. The hairy bit is coming up with a standard for what is called family friendly, in which case modeling it after some industry standard might be the simplest option. The method for how we present/lock content doesn't really need to comply with any standard, though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


